name: torch-runstats
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "torch-runstats" %}
{% set version = "0.2.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/t/torch_runstats/torch_runstats-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: bc7f32887103c820bd7cc710b9c476d1ec56a68a3ff9a42b9b56758bfb8afd97

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - pytorch

test:
  imports:
    - torch_runstats
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/mir-group/pytorch_runstats
  summary: Running/online statistics for PyTorch
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jan-janssen
